      "comment": "FORGERY (7) has a strong record this track and trip with three wins and two placings from seven starts. Hit the frame latest (31.10) when second at this track in a TG1-4W. Appeals as a leading chance in this. MICKEY HALLER (2) bolted in last time, scoring by 4.5 lengths in slick time (30.81) to take a TG1-4W in a new PB this course and distance. Should be in this for a long way. GIGGLE MONSTER (3) overcame a check in the run and hit the line hard to place (31.31) at this track over 530m in a TG1-4W. Expected to feature. VICTA HOWARD (8) has ability and can feature with the right run after missing a cheque here most recently.",
